Educational thinking: How to make "efighters" and "scumbags" get their own way - Xinhua English.news.cn
Three students from Lanzhou Jiaotong University wrote to the school leaders to reflect the confusion about the university exam, and proposed to increase the difficulty of the exam and change the type of exam questions, so that the exam truly reflects the students’ actual level.
Indeed, college exams have long been a "hot topic".
On a university campus, students come from all over the world, with different ability levels, combined with different levels of learning, with enormously different learning situations.
Assessment of groups with such diverse characteristics, it is inevitable that there will be different feelings.
Of course, if the exam questions are of a single type and a high repetition rate, and the questions are too simple, it will inevitably lead to another completely different feeling.
Students who do not work hardCOS may pass the test. If they think of other ways, they may achieve twice the result with half the effort.
As a result, "students" can pass the test without any input or even get high marks; "students" usually never miss classes, their assignments and notes are good, and their exams are not much higher than that of the "excellent status".
It seems that the students at Lanzhou Jiaotong University reported that the problems in the university examinations are not without cause, I believe this situation is not only in Lanzhou Jiaotong University.
In this sense, I would like to praise these three students who wrote directly.
In fact, everyone who has been to college knows that it is not uncommon to preempt共享 tests, seek various ways to "trick" test questions from teachers, try to delineate the scope of the test, and get "key tutoring" before the test. It is not uncommon to even carry cheat sheets and ask teachers to prove their valuable hand after the test.
In the author's view, as a teaching quality evaluation orientation, the qualification of a university examination depends on teachers' comprehensive grasp of teaching and learning, as well as scientific propositions based on this.
Entering the undergraduate level, majors begin to be subdivided, and many professional courses are based on basic knowledge.
There is no doubt that whether a comprehensive grasp of the basic knowledge points of a subject is the content to be examined in the university examination.
However, undergraduate knowledge is basically the basic theory and basic common sense. From a knowledge point of view, there is not much room for change, and it is basically fixed.
Just as some teachers said, "The basic knowledge of college mathematics 20 years ago is still being learnt, and it is still the key point."
However, the knowledge points remain basically unchanged, which does not mean that the test questions are single and repeated.
In many universities, the examination is generally into question sets, then senior teachers in the discipline make up the examination paper, and the examination papers are also attended by all the teachers who are responsible for the subject, so that the duplication of examination questions can be overcome to a certain extent.
However, it is necessary to draw up a set of examination questions that conform to the facts of teaching and learning. The questions are based on the overall situation of students' learning, and the difficulty is normally distributed. It is also necessary to comprehensively grasp the teaching situation and comprehensively analyze the level of student learning so that the examination propositions can have a dynamic grasp of difficulty and question type. It can not only highlight the basic knowledge examination, but also take into account the ability assessment, and at the same time, innovatively designed the question type.
Exams are the baton of university education. What kind of exams are required, students will have corresponding preparation plans. In the long run, it will affect the effectiveness of university education.
Lanzhou Jiaotong University attaches great importance to the letter of advice from students and has deployed a rectification plan throughout the school.
All teaching units are required to organize teachers to conduct seminars and post-course examination comparisons on self-checks, formulate examination paper propositions and related systems, and at the same time strengthen the supervision and inspection of the examination paper propositions and review links, refine the performance assessment, and strengthen the comprehensive assessment of all aspects of course teaching.
Mechanistically solving problems such as single type of examination questions and repeated questions is a problem that the university examination affairs need to face. Of course, there needs to be a corresponding system. However, it is󠄡ṣday troubles and required teachers to fully grasp the teaching situation, not only to understand the teaching content, but also the students' learning situation, both ends, teaching and learning will be more well connected, forming a positive interaction, and testing will also be more realistic, so that "cyclical masters" and "原始梦 Quins" will each have their own shares.
